perl-http-negotiate (Choose a variant to serve)

This package contains the HTTP::Negotiate module.
This module provides a complete implementation of the HTTP content
negotiation algorithm specified in draft-ietf-http-v11-spec-00.ps
chapter 12. Content negotiation allows for the selection of a
preferred content representation based upon attributes of the
content and the negotiable variants and the value of the various
Accept* header fields in the request.

HOME: https://metacpan.org/pod/HTTP::Negotiate

======================================================================
REQUIRES: perl-http-message 

